Description:
At the end of the hall you find a large stone statue of an imp.

Although the placement of this statue is suspicious, it can be clearly seen that it is used as an altar of some kind.

You've found imps before wandering around freely and this statue may have something to do with it.
DescriptionAction: What do you want to do?
